Command: orchestrator diff review
Status: correction applied
Notes: The first implementation made `macos-check` depend on fail-fast Linux
hygiene tools, which could break hosted macOS where Taplo, shfmt, typos,
markdownlint-cli2, or actionlint are not installed by the native bootstrap.
The orchestrator corrected the recipes so Linux/Nix remains fail-fast, while
Darwin runs those hygiene tools when present and otherwise prints explicit
non-Linux skip messages. SwiftFormat and SwiftLint remain required on Darwin
through `macos-swiftformat` and `macos-swiftlint`.

